OL,5, A teacher who groomed a 15-year-old boy
OL,6, and had sex with him has been banned   
OL,7, from the classroom indefinitely.       
OL,9,FKandice Barber, 38, of Wendover,       
OL,10,FBuckinghamshire, was sentenced to six  
OL,11,Fyears and two months in prison.        
OL,13,FThe Secretary of State for Education   
OL,14,Fhas now prohibited her from her        
OL,15,Fprofession on a recommendation from the
OL,16,FTeaching Regulation Agency. (TRA)      
OL,18,FThe panel concluded she had a "callous 
OL,19,Fand selfish disregard for her pupil's  
OL,20,Fwell-being".                           
